	(37200, 2, 0, 'Charge!!!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16971, 'Muradin Bronzebeard - SAY_INTRO_ALLIANCE_5'),
	(37200, 3, 0, '%s gasps for air.', 16, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16975, 'Muradin Bronzebeard - SAY_OUTRO_ALLIANCE_1'),
	(37200, 4, 0, 'That was Saurfang\'s boy - the Horde commander at the Wrath Gate. Such a tragic end...', 12, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16976, 'Muradin Bronzebeard - SAY_OUTRO_ALLIANCE_2'),
	(37200, 5, 0, 'What in the... There, in the distance!', 12, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16977, 'Muradin Bronzebeard - SAY_OUTRO_ALLIANCE_3'),
	(37200, 6, 0, 'A Horde Zeppelin flies up to the rise.', 16, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Muradin Bronzebeard - SAY_OUTRO_ALLIANCE_4'),
	(37200, 7, 0, 'Soldiers, fall in! Looks like the Horde are comin\' to take another shot!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16978, 'Muradin Bronzebeard - SAY_OUTRO_ALLIANCE_5'),
	(37200, 8, 0, 'The Zeppelin docks, and High Overlord Saurfang hops out, confronting the Alliance soldiers and Muradin', 16, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Muradin Bronzebeard - SAY_OUTRO_ALLIANCE_6'),
	(37200, 9, 0, 'Don\'t force me hand, orc. We can\'t let ye pass.', 12, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16972, 'Muradin Bronzebeard - SAY_OUTRO_ALLIANCE_7'),
	(37200, 10, 0, 'I... I can\'t do it. Get back on yer ship and we\'ll spare yer life.', 12, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16973, 'Muradin Bronzebeard - SAY_OUTRO_ALLIANCE_9'),
	(37200, 11, 0, 'A mage portal from Stormwind appears between the two and Varian Wrynn and Jaina Proudmoore emerge.', 16, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Muradin Bronzebeard - SAY_OUTRO_ALLIANCE_10'),
	(37200, 12, 0, 'Right away, yer majesty!', 12, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16979, 'Muradin Bronzebeard - SAY_OUTRO_ALLIANCE_21'),
	(37200, 13, 0, 'Could it be, Lord Fordring? If Bolvar lives, mayhap there is hope fer peace between the Alliance and the Horde. We must reach the top o\' this cursed place and free the paladin!', 12, 0, 0, 6, 0, 16980, 'Muradin Bronzebeard - SAY_SAURFANG_INTRO_2'),
	(37200, 14, 0, 'Prepare the Skybreaker fer an aerial assault on the citadel!', 14, 0, 0, 5, 0, 16981, 'Muradin Bronzebeard - SAY_SAURFANG_INTRO_3'),
	(37200, 15, 0, 'Heroes, ye must fight yer way to a clear extraction point within Icecrown. We\'ll try an\' rendezvous on the ramparts!', 14, 0, 0, 22, 0, 16982, 'Muradin Bronzebeard - SAY_SAURFANG_INTRO_4'),
	(37217, 0, 0, '%s cries out with a loud, baying howl!', 41, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Precious - EMOTE_PRECIOUS_ZOMBIES'),
