	(12435, 3, 0, 'If I fall into the abyss I\'ll take all of you mortals with me...', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 8278, 'razorgore SAY_DEATH'),
	(12717, 0, 0, 'Are you sure that you are ready? If we do not have a group of your allies to aid us, we will surely fail.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'muglash SAY_MUG_START1'),
	(12717, 1, 0, 'This will be a though fight, $N. Follow me closely.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'muglash SAY_MUG_START2'),
	(12717, 2, 0, 'This is the brazier, $N. Put it out. Vorsha is a beast, worthy of praise from no one!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'muglash SAY_MUG_BRAZIER'),
	(12717, 3, 0, 'Now we must wait. It won\'t be long before the naga realize what we have done.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'muglash SAY_MUG_BRAZIER_WAIT'),
	(12717, 4, 0, 'Be on your guard, $N!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'muglash SAY_MUG_ON_GUARD'),
	(12717, 5, 0, 'Perhaps we will get a moment to rest. But I will not give up until we have faced off against Vorsha!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'muglash SAY_MUG_REST'),
	(12717, 6, 0, 'We have done it!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'muglash SAY_MUG_DONE'),
	(12717, 7, 0, 'You have my deepest gratitude. I thank you.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'muglash SAY_MUG_GRATITUDE'),
	(12717, 8, 0, 'I am going to patrol the area for a while longer and ensure that things are truly safe.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'muglash SAY_MUG_PATROL'),
	(12717, 9, 0, 'Please return to Zoram\'gar and report our success to the Warsong runner.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'muglash SAY_MUG_RETURN'),
	(13020, 0, 0, 'Too late...friends. Nefarius\' corruption has taken hold. I cannot...control myself.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 8281, 'vaelastrasz SAY_LINE1'),
	(13020, 1, 0, 'I beg you Mortals, flee! Flee before I lose all control. The Black Fire rages within my heart. I must release it!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 8282, 'vaelastrasz SAY_LINE2'),
	(13020, 2, 0, 'FLAME! DEATH! DESTRUCTION! COWER MORTALS BEFORE THE WRATH OF LORD....NO! I MUST FIGHT THIS!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 8283, 'vaelastrasz SAY_LINE3'),
	(13020, 3, 0, 'Nefarius\' hate has made me stronger than ever before. You should have fled, while you could, mortals! The fury of Blackrock courses through my veins!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 8285, 'vaelastrasz SAY_HALFLIFE'),
	(13020, 4, 0, 'Forgive me $N, your death only adds to my failure.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 8284, 'vaelastrasz SAY_KILLTARGET'),
