	(28070, 27, 0, 'Hold everything! The Aesir and Vanir went to war? Why?', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14271, 'brann SAY_EVENT_END_16'),
	(28070, 28, 0, 'This Loken sounds like a nasty character. Glad we don\'t have to worry about the likes of him anymore. So if I\'m understanding you lads the original Earthen eventually woke up from this statis. And by that time this destabily-whatever had turned them into our brother dwarfs. Or at least dwarf ancestors. Hm?', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14272, 'brann SAY_EVENT_END_18'),
