	(67990, 19, 0, 'Ahhh, so the grand lady of the Kirin Tor wants a fight, does she?', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(67990, 20, 0, 'Alas, the Zandalari trolls have already claimed and fortified it.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(67990, 21, 0, 'Brothers and sisters of the Horde! Enemies surround us on all sides! Your courage in weeks to come will be the difference between victory and defeat.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(67990, 22, 0, 'Champion! Again you are at the forefront of a Horde triumph. And once more I am in your debt.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(67990, 23, 0, 'Champion! Our campaign is reaching a climax: We are at the very threshold of the Thunder King\'s palace. It is time to knock down his front door.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(67990, 24, 0, 'Champion, I need you to lead a ground assault and take down that barrier from within!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(67990, 25, 0, 'Champion, you have brought glory to the Horde. Your unshakable will has secured our position here. Now, the true work begins.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(67990, 26, 0, 'Do it.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(67990, 27, 0, 'Elsia is waiting for you, champion.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(67990, 28, 0, 'Heroes, take the towers, turn the guns onto that proto-drake, and blast it from the sky!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(67990, 29, 0, 'I have selected a landing site for our forces: a small peninsula to our east that is easily defended.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(67990, 30, 0, 'I will deal with Proudmoore.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(67990, 31, 0, 'In good time, my pandaren friend. In good time.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(67990, 32, 0, 'Incredible work. I knew the Shado-Pan would make excellent allies.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(67990, 33, 0, 'Lady.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(67990, 34, 0, 'Likewise. Sylvanas and I have both sent ships to support Vol\'jin\'s revolution.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(67990, 35, 0, 'Mount up and rendezvous with Scout Captain Elsia. She is organizing an elite group of rangers to accompany you. May the light of the sun shine upon you.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(67990, 36, 0, 'Nonsense. This is where I belong.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(67990, 37, 0, 'Rangers - to me! We have broken their lines!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(67990, 38, 0, 'Regardless, we have delivered a terrible blow to the Thunder King today. Horde metalsmiths can begin studying mogu fabrication techniques immediately.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(67990, 39, 0, 'Regroup behind the wards, everyone. They will counter-attack... but we will be ready.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(67990, 40, 0, 'Rommath, establish a perimeter. Aethas, begin placing the sentry wards. Kethiel, unload the shelters and supplies.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(67990, 41, 0, 'Some of you will need to stay behind to hold the beachhead.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(67990, 42, 0, 'Speak to me when you are ready to launch the assault!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(67990, 43, 0, 'Strategy, Dark Lady. We should repurpose the shore defenses.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(67990, 44, 0, 'That is precisely why I wish to conserve our strength today.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(67990, 45, 0, 'They\'re protecting it with a powerful spirit barrier. We will need to disable it before our ships can land.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(67990, 46, 0, 'This means he\'s completely unhinged.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(67990, 47, 0, 'Victory to the Sin\'dorei! And another triumph for the Horde.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(67990, 48, 0, 'Well done. The first brigade has made landfall.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(67990, 49, 0, 'With the help of the Shado-Pan and this beast you recovered, I believe we can infiltrate and disable the Thunder King\'s armory.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(67990, 50, 0, 'Yes?', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(67990, 51, 0, 'You have earned my trust hero. This will be your most dangerous task yet: To steal the secrets of the Thunder King from the very heart of his lair. I wish you the best of luck.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(69478, 0, 0, 'Brothers and sisters of the Horde! Enemies surround us on all sides! Your courage in weeks to come will be the difference between victory and defeat.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(69478, 1, 0, 'Rommath, establish a perimeter. Aethas, begin placing the sentry wards. Kethiel, unload the shelters and supplies.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(69617, 0, 0, 'Damn their hides. Rangers! Hold this position!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(69617, 1, 0, 'Gather the wounded. Withdraw to the harbor.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(69617, 2, 0, 'I must protect my sovereign people.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(69617, 3, 0, 'One problem at a time, people. Focus on the Zandalari!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(69617, 4, 0, 'Proudmoore! You will release my people from the Violet Hold, or I will cut you down myself!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(69617, 5, 0, 'Rangers. Lower your weapons.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(69617, 6, 0, 'The Sunreavers knew NOTHING of Garrosh\'s raid on Darnassus!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(69617, 7, 0, 'Do it.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(69617, 8, 0, 'I will deal with Proudmoore.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(69617, 9, 0, 'Lady.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(69617, 10, 0, 'That is precisely why I wish to conserve our strength today.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(69742, 0, 0, 'Ah! Champion, we were just talking about you.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(69742, 1, 0, 'Surely you agree that decisive action wins wars, Lord Zhu.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(69742, 2, 0, 'The sheer audacity of the plan is exactly what intrigues me. If we breech the shipyard, we will deprive the mogu of further Zandalari reinforcements.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(69797, 0, 0, 'You have earned my trust hero. This will be your most dangerous task yet: To steal the secrets of the Thunder King from the very heart of his lair. I wish you the best of luck.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(69799, 0, 0, 'Aethas, I want our best archmages studying this device at once. We have so much to learn.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(69799, 1, 0, 'Blood as a power source - a very powerful form of life magic. The work of the titans, perhaps? How does it work?', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(69799, 2, 0, 'Thank you, champion! The Horde may be on the verge of crisis, but your actions on these shores have ensured our continued survival and prosperity no matter what comes next.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(69799, 3, 0, 'What have you brought back? Ah! Fascinating.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron');
