	(70055, 3, 0, 'Regroup behind the wards, everyone. They will counter-attack... but we will be ready.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(70371, 0, 0, 'Aethas, leave us for a moment.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(70371, 1, 0, 'Alas, the Zandalari trolls have already claimed and fortified it.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(70371, 2, 0, 'Anar\'alah belore, hero. Good luck.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(70371, 3, 0, 'Brothers and sisters of the Horde! Enemies surround us on all sides! Your courage in weeks to come will be the difference between victory and defeat.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(70371, 4, 0, 'But, in defeating him, we must seek out the source of his great power. We must claim it for ourselves, as leverage against our "Warchief."', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(70371, 5, 0, 'Champion, I need you to lead a ground assault and take down that barrier from within!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(70371, 6, 0, 'Enough talk. You know how precarious our position is. Between the Alliance and the Thunder King, only with the help of heroes like you can we hope to succeed here.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(70371, 7, 0, 'Ha-hah! It will feel good to bloody my blade again. Against Alliance or mogu, does not matter to me.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(70371, 8, 0, 'Heads up!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(70371, 9, 0, 'Hero, you have served the Horde nobly across many campaigns. I feel I can take you into confidence.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(70371, 10, 0, 'I have selected a landing site for our forces: a small peninsula to our east that is easily defended.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(70371, 11, 0, 'In the event of an uprising, we must be prepared.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(70371, 12, 0, 'Mount up and rendezvous with Scout Captain Elsia. She is organizing an elite group of rangers to accompany you. May the light of the sun shine upon you.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(70371, 13, 0, 'Our Warchief\'s campaign across Kalimdor and Pandaria is pulling the Horde apart at the seams.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(70371, 14, 0, 'Rommath, establish a perimeter. Aethas, begin placing the sentry wards. Kethiel, unload the shelters and supplies.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(70371, 15, 0, 'They\'re protecting it with a powerful spirit barrier. We will need to disable it before our ships can land.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(70371, 16, 0, 'Victory to the Sin\'dorei! And another triumph for the Horde.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(70371, 17, 0, 'We are here to fight the Thunder King. Justice demands it, and Hellscream is too preoccupied at Domination Point to pay attention here.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Lor\'themar Theron'),
	(69433, 0, 0, 'Go now, to Ihgaluk Crag. I will apply the second half of your illusion once you have arrived.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Magistrix Saia'),
	(69686, 0, 0, 'It looks like the scavengers may be sending a large party out into the swamp soon. Tell the archmage to be ready.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Magistrix Sanal'),
	(69686, 1, 0, 'Let the archmage know that everything is under control here at Ihgaluk. I\'ll have another report in a few days.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Magistrix Sanal'),
	(69310, 0, 0, 'It looks like the scavengers may be sending a large party out into the swamp soon. Tell the archmage to be ready.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Magistrix Vesara'),
	(69310, 1, 0, 'Let the archmage know that everything is under control here at Ihgaluk. I\'ll have another report in a few days.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Magistrix Vesara'),
	(69697, 0, 0, 'ATTEMPTING TO RECOVER FROM EMBARRASSING MALFUNCTION...', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Malfunctioning Silver Covenant Construct'),
	(69697, 1, 0, 'REBOOTING...', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Malfunctioning Silver Covenant Construct'),
	(69697, 2, 0, 'RECOVERY FAILED. INCREMENTING SHAME PARAMETER. RETURNING TO BASE.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Malfunctioning Silver Covenant Construct'),
	(69697, 3, 0, 'SYSTEM ONLINE. FEELING MUCH BETTER NOW.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Malfunctioning Silver Covenant Construct'),
	(69289, 0, 0, 'REBOOTING...', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Malfunctioning Sunreaver Construct'),
	(69289, 1, 0, 'SYSTEM ONLINE. FEELING MUCH BETTER NOW.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Malfunctioning Sunreaver Construct'),
	(69286, 0, 0, 'Came to the wrong place, ya did.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Master Caller'),
	(69286, 1, 0, 'Don\'t be makin\' da big one mad, mon!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Master Caller'),
	(69286, 2, 0, 'Too late for ya to be runnin\' away now, mon!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Master Caller'),
	(69286, 3, 0, 'We gonna\' feed ya to the big one!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Master Caller'),
	(69286, 4, 0, 'Ya barely be fit tah\' feed to de big one.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Master Caller'),
	(69485, 0, 0, 'Champion, without your help I would\'ve died in that swamp. I owe you my very life.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Scout Captain Elsia'),
	(69485, 1, 0, 'Destroy the spirit mask to bring down the barrier!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Scout Captain Elsia'),
	(69485, 2, 0, 'Good work, hero. Let\'s move on.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Scout Captain Elsia'),
	(69485, 3, 0, 'I do not like the look of that troll. Be careful!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Scout Captain Elsia'),
	(69485, 4, 0, 'I will cover the flanks. Gather up our explosives and get them to the wall. Hurry!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Scout Captain Elsia'),
	(69485, 5, 0, 'It is chaos out there, <name>! The siege has begun but our heavy explosives never made it to the wall.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Scout Captain Elsia'),
	(69485, 6, 0, 'No. Not good.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Scout Captain Elsia'),
	(69485, 7, 0, 'Our only hope of getting out of here alive is to take the town.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Scout Captain Elsia'),
	(69485, 8, 0, 'The entrance is barricaded. Break it down!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Scout Captain Elsia'),
	(69485, 9, 0, 'The shield - it is down! We did it!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Scout Captain Elsia'),
	(69485, 10, 0, 'They are protecting that mask. It must be the source of the barrier. Destroy it!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Scout Captain Elsia'),
	(69485, 11, 0, 'They are pulling back, but we cannot let up now.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Scout Captain Elsia'),
	(69485, 12, 0, 'We were not safe at all. They were waiting for us. Our forces are scattered throughout the swamp, and we are alone behind enemy lines!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Scout Captain Elsia'),
	(69485, 13, 0, 'You make this look easy.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Scout Captain Elsia'),
	(69565, 0, 0, 'A Shado-Pan contact will be waiting to meet you behind the mines. Good luck!!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Scout Captain Elsia'),
	(69565, 1, 0, 'Rangers - shatter the hinges. Wedge the doors open!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Scout Captain Elsia'),
	(69565, 2, 0, 'This way - the Zandalari are falling back!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Scout Captain Elsia'),
	(69565, 3, 0, 'Be ready to dogfight in the air. Jump from mount to mount if you have to!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Scout Captain Elsia'),
	(69565, 4, 0, 'Do you think you can ride it?', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Scout Captain Elsia'),
	(69565, 5, 0, 'Good, you are here.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Scout Captain Elsia'),
	(69565, 6, 0, 'My Lord Regent - you should not be so close to the front lines.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Scout Captain Elsia'),
	(69565, 7, 0, 'The charges are placed. Hero - you may have the honor.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Scout Captain Elsia'),
	(69565, 8, 0, 'The Regent Lord will want a full report. Let\'s get you back to camp - you have earned a rest.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Scout Captain Elsia'),
	(69565, 9, 0, 'This creature you\'ve recovered is immune to the lightning strikes that protect the island.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Scout Captain Elsia'),
	(69565, 10, 0, 'Very good! Once you take to the skies, the Zandalari will try to stop you.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Scout Captain Elsia'),
	(69565, 11, 0, 'What... what did they DO to that troll!?', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Scout Captain Elsia'),
	(69565, 12, 0, 'Your plan worked! The two of you accomplished the work of an army.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Scout Captain Elsia'),
	(69620, 0, 0, 'My Lord!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Scout Captain Elsia'),
	(69620, 1, 0, 'Regent Lord - more Zandalari approach from the mines!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Scout Captain Elsia'),
	(69620, 2, 0, 'Good, you are here.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Scout Captain Elsia'),
	(69620, 3, 0, 'Regent Lord! Everyone is in position, and the Shado-Pan are inside, but...', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Scout Captain Elsia'),
	(69620, 4, 0, 'The Alliance is waiting for us just across the courtyard.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Scout Captain Elsia'),
	(69530, 0, 0, 'Arise, Nalak! Protect our beloved emperor.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Shan Bu'),
